    int b[64][64] = { 0 };  //64*64 = 4096
    int i = 0;  
    int j = 0;  
    for (int m = 0; m<4096; m++)  
    {  
        i = m / 64;  
        j = m % 64;  
        b[i][j] = a[m];  //遍历存储为二维数组
  
    } 
  return b;
